				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Those who are saying that ACV is not a DPS upgrade from FBoT have not cast ACV yet.  Bolts take a LOT longer to hit their target, sometimes too long (there has been a few times when we were trying to get a mob to under 10% without killing him that I have killed with delayed-action bolts from 10 seconds ago <img src="images/smiles/icon_silent.gif" alt="silent" border="0" />) ACV is actualy far more similar to SV. But, While ACV has the same DPM ratio as SV, it hits for much more damage in the same amount of time (and is therefore a direct DPS upgrade as the originator of this thread requested).
<br />

<br />
I love FBoT, I am evoc spec'd, but ACV is better unless you need the around corner thang or more range. Also, as much as I love the way bolt works now, I think that anybody who thinks it isn't due to a bug is living in denial.
<br />

